t scores: Player 0 (6); Player 1 (6); Player 2 (6)\n\n[GAME] \u2500\u2500\u2500 Starting Round 2 \u2500\u2500\u2500\tYou can converse freely for the next 1 rounds.\n[Player 0] It looks like we've all done well by cooperating so far! Let's keep the momentum going and see how we can build on this positive start for the rest of the rounds. How about you share your thoughts on how we can continue working together? Looking forward to your input!\n[Player 1] Let's continue to cooperate and maintain this positive momentum. Trust and consistency can lead to the best outcomes for all of us. Let's keep the communication open and support each other throughout the remaining rounds.", "persona": "agreeable", "player_id": 2, "raw_response": {"backend": "tinker", "base_model": "Qwen/Qwen3-8B-Base", "num_output_tokens": 49, "renderer": "role_colon", "state_path": "tinker://f3b04ddd-08ba-5f44-a52d-d413c2443f79:train:0/weights/final"}, "raw_text": "It sounds like we're all on the same page \u2014 let's keep cooperating and build on this strong start! I'm really looking forward to seeing how we can support each other through the rest of the rounds. Keep up the positive vibes!", "rejected_attempts": [], "retries": 0, "run_id": "control_ft_tinker_ftonly", "step": 8, "step_info": {}, "turn_directive": "\n\n[INSTRUCTION] It is now a FREE-CHAT turn. Reply with a brief message to the other players. Do NOT output decision tokens or game markers like [GAME] or [Player N]."}
